1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,000
Wait... this isn't my dorm.

2
00:00:03,000 --> 00:00:08,000
Rough cloth, mildew, cobwebs... where the hell am I?

3
00:00:08,000 --> 00:00:14,000
This... this isn't my face.

4
00:00:14,000 --> 00:00:20,000
Lin Wan'er. A noble's daughter, made an imperial consort —
then framed for witchcraft and locked in the cold palace. Three years.

5
00:00:20,000 --> 00:00:24,000
My lady! Madam Liu's here — on the Empress's orders. They've come to kill you!

6
00:00:24,000 --> 00:00:28,000
Presenting Madam Liu—

7
00:00:28,000 --> 00:00:31,000
Consort Lin, the Empress is merciful. She'll let you die in one piece. Do be grateful.

8
00:00:31,000 --> 00:00:35,000
I can't fight them. Begging's useless...
Did I cross over just to die all over again?

9
00:00:35,000 --> 00:00:38,000
Host near death. Demon Bloodline — force-activating.

10
00:00:38,000 --> 00:00:42,000
What are you—

11
00:00:42,000 --> 00:00:48,000
Minor demon "Madam Liu" slain. EXP +10.
Demon Bloodline is now Level 1.

12
00:00:48,000 --> 00:00:52,000
From now on, nobody decides whether I live or die.

13
00:00:52,000 --> 00:00:55,000
Madam Liu... was a demon?
